# 🍳 **FoodHive — AI-Powered Recipe Website**

## 📖 **Overview**

FoodHive is a fully automated recipe website that publishes **12 fresh recipes daily** using AI. Built with Next.js and powered by Gemini 2.5 Flash, it features:

- ✅ **12 Recipe Categories** (Breakfast, Lunch, Dinner, Desserts, etc.)
- ✅ **Auto-Publishing** — 1 recipe every 2 hours (12/day, 360/month)
- ✅ **Complete Recipe Data** — Ingredients, instructions, nutrition, tips
- ✅ **Beautiful UI** — Orange + cream theme inspired by modern food apps
- ✅ **SEO Optimized** — Static generation with Next.js
- ✅ **Zero Cost** — GitHub + Vercel + Activepieces free tiers

---

## 🎨 **Design Theme**

Based on the uploaded food delivery app design:

- **Primary Color:** `#FF6B35` (Orange)
- **Secondary Color:** `#FFD93D` (Yellow)
- **Background:** `#FFF8E7` (Cream)
- **Accent Colors:** Green `#6BCF7F`, Brown `#5D4037`
- **Fonts:** Playfair Display (headings) + Poppins (body)

