## 🗂️ **File Locations Guide**

When copying files to your project:

### **Root Directory:**
```
/foodhive/
  ├── package.json          ← Paste here
  ├── next.config.js        ← Paste here
  ├── .gitignore            ← Paste here
  ├── README.md             ← Paste here
  └── ACTIVEPIECES_FLOW.json ← Paste here
```

### **Lib Directory:**
```
/foodhive/lib/
  └── data.js               ← Create lib/ folder, paste here
```

### **Styles Directory:**
```
/foodhive/styles/
  └── globals.css           ← Create styles/ folder, paste here
```

### **Pages Directory:**
```
/foodhive/pages/
  ├── _app.js              ← Create pages/ folder
  ├── index.js             ← Homepage
  ├── recipes/
  │   ├── index.js         ← Create recipes/ subfolder
  │   └── [slug].js        ← Recipe detail page
  └── categories/
      └── [category].js    ← Create categories/ subfolder
```

### **Data Directory:**
```
/foodhive/data/
  └── recipes/             ← Create empty data/recipes/ folder
                             (will auto-fill via automation)
```

