## 📝 **Recipe JSON Structure**

Each auto-generated recipe follows this structure:

```json
{
  "slug": "breakfast-fluffy-pancakes",
  "title": "Fluffy Pancakes",
  "category": "breakfast",
  "categoryName": "Breakfast Recipes",
  "categoryIcon": "🍳",
  "prepTime": "10 min",
  "cookTime": "15 min",
  "totalTime": "25 min",
  "servings": 4,
  "difficulty": "Easy",
  "cuisine": "American",
  "image1": "https://images.pexels.com/...",
  "image2": "https://images.pexels.com/...",
  "description": "Light, fluffy pancakes...",
  "ingredients": [
    { "item": "Flour", "amount": "2 cups", "notes": "sifted" }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    { "step": 1, "title": "Mix dry", "text": "...", "time": "2 min" }
  ],
  "nutritionTable": {
    "calories": "320 kcal",
    "protein": "8g",
    "carbs": "45g",
    "fat": "12g"
  },
  "tags": ["breakfast", "pancakes", "easy"],
  "tips": ["Let batter rest 5 minutes..."],
  "rating": 4.8,
  "reviews": 342,
  "publishedAt": "2026-01-15T10:00:00.000Z"
}
```

